{"type": "article", "id": 21221, "title": "玻璃餐具“鱼”", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-25T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606161355ZnNRVvDmglaGuBSw.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套名为“鱼”的餐具来自意大利设计师 paola navone 和比利时家具品牌 Serax，玻璃瓶和餐盘都借用了鱼的形状和鱼鳞纹，清爽中透着趣味。设计师从美国 20 世纪 30 年代的大萧条时期的玻璃制造工艺中获得灵感，除了略带绿色的透明颜色外，他还使用了翠绿色和白色，倒有点接近玉的感觉，带着一份温润感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150838YwyQ7CAf8D6hdvPj.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"733\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89608802\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150839axSU5y3VN4nO7ZHB.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"794\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.97066015\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261508404JOcXpHjCbP1IRAi.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"649\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79339853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150840Ly15hmBwcgH7FTI6.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"528\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64547677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}